             sworn.</p>
               <p>I live in Primrose-street, an apothecary; I have known him from his birth; always a very industrious clever young man, and very honest.</p>
               <p>What is his character as to humanity? - Quite a humane man, quite so.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860531-28-person429">
                  DOROTHY
                   HANDLEBY
               <interp inst="t17860531-28-person429" type="surname" value="HANDLEBY"></interp>
