             sworn.</p>
               <p>I have known him twenty-five years; I lived sixteen years in that family; he was almost continually, both as a child and youth and a man, backwards and forwards; with respect to his general character, as to humanity and good-nature, all that has been said of him by the last witness is exceedingly just; I never knew him do an ill-natured action; I never saw him, either when a child or a youth, to torture a fly.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860531-28-person430">
                  THOMAS
                   GARDNER
               <interp inst="t17860531-28-person430" type="surname" value="GARDNER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17860531-28-person430" type="given" value="THOMAS"></interp>
