               <p>I live in Old-street, Cloth-fair; I am a cabinet-maker; I have known him five years and a half; he is a particularly humane benevolent man; I have had some opportunities of knowing him in that respect, and always took him to be so.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17860531-28-person431">
                  CHARLES
                   MIDDLETON
